{"tid":2058874,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"(厲害了你的國)「戰狼」船員回國無門海上漂，發帖求救反遭封殺","createTime":"2020-06-10T13:25:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-10T15:45:35.000Z","uid":38539,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"1203091e8341f727ac030c24a61cd98941c49c9e","tid":2058874,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T13:25:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/Ys36tCB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FYs36tCB.jpg&h=cd2adea6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中共為「防疫」封堵海外中國人回國，數萬中國船員被困海上，處境悲慘，陸續有人崩潰自殺。近日，中國船員的求救帖子引發關注。其中包括一個曾經的「戰狼」，當初叫囂參軍鎮壓「港獨」，如今發帖向「祖國」求救卻遭微博封殺。<br />\n<br />\n6月8日，一個網名「Leooo濤」的微博用戶發帖求助，自稱一名受困英國海域的中國船員，已經超過百日沒有上岸了。和自已一樣被困英國的，還有6百多名中國籍船員。眼看著其它國家的船員陸續被接回國，而中國船員們「包機回國」的計劃一次次落空，在船上如同坐牢，除了每天兩次體溫檢測，所有活動都被取消。<br />\n<br />\n帖子還說，這些中國船員是為了生活背井離鄉，支付不起天價機票，而且護照都在中共官方的人事部手上，想自己走都走不了。家中的親人都在期盼著他們回家，因此請求中共政府能夠「重視」他們的處境。<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/zSVgOQh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FzSVgOQh.jpg&h=bc03bc0a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「Leooo濤」的求救帖。（網絡圖片）<br />\n<br />\n不過，有網友翻出「Leooo濤」當初仇視香港反送中運動的帖子，大大削減了網友們對其求救帖的同情。<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/TIb2Y95.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FTIb2Y95.jpg&h=294a19b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黨媒《環球時報》記者在香港機場被示威者制服時，「Leooo濤」發帖要參軍鎮壓所謂「港獨」。（網絡圖片）<br />\n<br />\n還有網友貼出截圖譏諷道，「Leooo濤」的求救帖已經引起微博的「高度重視」，微博啟動了「圖片識別和諧大法」，對求救帖的截圖予以封殺。有人將截圖倒轉後，才上傳成功。<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/YFQYHrl.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FYFQYHrl.jpg&h=7740d6b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「Leooo濤」求救帖的截圖在微博遭封殺。（網頁截圖）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ntdtv.com/b5/2020/06/09/a102866906.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ntdtv.com%2Fb5%2F2020%2F06%2F09%2Fa102866906.html&d=TNVh%2FXBsTmD9bRjMILuVazDyw%2Fr9SRfH8QBX8OZV2FM%3D&h=906faa04\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ntdtv.com/b5/2020/06/09/a102866906.html</a>"},{"pid":"52a1be69e0efd01a5f709f7a565a850dd0e80d19","tid":2058874,"uid":191453,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T13:28:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U8yY5Sr.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU8yY5Sr.gif&h=53de54c4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a110b6d82628f869e7edea561a98200a2fdc290d","tid":2058874,"uid":62527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T13:29:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4e2d774a789c112681bccf2d971bb2d574ce517","tid":2058874,"uid":3122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T13:29:47.000Z","msg":"截圖倒轉後，才上傳成功"},{"pid":"3911fb7d463036d527995a075b274ef92fc86316","tid":2058874,"uid":290883,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T13:29:56.000Z","msg":"死撚咗佢啦，完全冇存在價值！"},{"pid":"9b2e3d44abd6d01349866f02dcb0bcbdf57f6e63","tid":2058874,"uid":69994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T13:30:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a699dd25b48ebd6e626325b0e6af34132349680b","tid":2058874,"uid":294919,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T13:31:34.000Z","msg":"呢幾個月真係見識到好多回力鏢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hk